{"data":[{"date":"14:05 15/08","title":"HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o danh ti\u1ebfng L'Equipe (Ph\u00e1p) v\u1eeba loan tin r\u1eb1ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Zinedine Zidane mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chia tay Real Madrid, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn Man Utd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t thay t\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1eefa d\u00f2ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u lung lay do th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p\u00a0BL\u0110\u00a0Man Utd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, th\u00ec Zidane s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/zidane-den-mu-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" \u1edf MU m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang ng\u1ed3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p HLV th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 \"\u0111\u00f3ng th\u1ebf\" Benitez v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ban \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi Real trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00ecm HLV\u00a0m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng Zizou \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0m HLV\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Zidane (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1eafm vai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd cho HLV Ancelotti \u1edf Bernabeu). K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \"Zizou \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebf\" \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Zidane b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Real ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hattrick th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh h\u1ed3i g\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB m\u00e0 Zidane t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zidane, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi L\u00e3o b\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 L\u0110B\u0110 Qatar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng m\u1eddi HLV 46 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng theo tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb t\u1edd L'Equire, Zidane l\u1ea1i h\u1ee9ng th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Man Utd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Old Trafford trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd do thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. Ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n, Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 gi\u00f4ng b\u00e3o \u1edf c\u00e1c CLB \u00f4ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, MU g\u1eb7p may khi th\u1eafng Leicester 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai kh\u00e1c, Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League 2018/19. V\u00e0 Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft, \u0111\u01b0a vinh quang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho, MU ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 cho HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen-voi-phat-bieu-ve-pogba-172-194533.html\">Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-thua-xa-man-city-va-liverpool-172-194512.html\">M.U thua xa Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca-172-194472.html\">MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ander-herrera-goi-y-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-194468.html\">Ander Herrera mang tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/darmian-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu-172-194460.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>T\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)</p>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2399","checkdouble":"194534"},{"date":"14:21 15/08","title":"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/chan-sut-son-heungmin-canh-bao-dong-doi-truoc-them-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan t\u1ea1i ASIAD&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau khi anh v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng Tottenham gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3y v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ban \u0111\u1ea7u, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 sau khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Tuy v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 xin ph\u00e9p ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Tottenham bay th\u1eb3ng sang T\u00e2y Java t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngay sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Newcastle.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Chan-sut-Son-Heung-min-nhac-nho-dong-doi-truoc-them-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Son Heung-Min mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xem m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea5m HCV 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Son Heung-min c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 1 trong 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hwang Ui-Jo c\u1ee7a Gamba Osaka v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Jo Hyeon-Woo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Anh v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111i m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i xem m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng b\u1ecb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ea1 \u1edf World Cup, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do s\u1edbm c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Indonesia, Son Heung-min cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 ASIAD tr\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn bay \u0111\u1ebfn Indonesia v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cho h\u1ecd l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn h\u1ecd c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min t\u1edbi v\u1edbi ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Theo lu\u1eadt H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, m\u1ecdi nam c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tu\u1ed5i 27 song v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh HCV ch\u00e2u \u00c1 hay Olympic.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2398","checkdouble":"194535"},{"date":"15:00 15/08","title":"Th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/thong-tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-xuan-truong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m th\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xuan Truong\" title=\"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/thong-tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-xuan-truong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL b\u1ecb \u0111au \u1edf ch\u00e2n l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean lo ng\u1ea1i anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m - Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo thay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb l\u00fd do chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch th\u00eam v\u00ec l\u00fd do thay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi&nbsp;HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0 nh\u1eadp h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, so v\u1edbi Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park tung H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t &quot;s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda&quot; gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tuy\u00ean Quang v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Nepal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho &lsquo;\u0111\u00e0n em&rsquo; C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:&#10;16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2397","checkdouble":"194537"},{"date":"15:07 15/08","title":"Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o danh ti\u1ebfng L'Equipe (Ph\u00e1p) v\u1eeba loan tin r\u1eb1ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Zinedine Zidane mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chia tay Real Madrid, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn Man Utd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t thay t\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1eefa d\u00f2ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u lung lay do th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p\u00a0BL\u0110\u00a0Man Utd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, th\u00ec Zidane s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/zidane-den-mu-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" \u1edf MU m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang ng\u1ed3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p HLV th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 \"\u0111\u00f3ng th\u1ebf\" Benitez v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ban \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi Real trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00ecm HLV\u00a0m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng Zizou \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0m HLV\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Zidane (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1eafm vai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd cho HLV Ancelotti \u1edf Bernabeu). K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \"Zizou \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebf\" \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Zidane b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Real ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hattrick th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh h\u1ed3i g\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB m\u00e0 Zidane t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zidane, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi L\u00e3o b\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 L\u0110B\u0110 Qatar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng m\u1eddi HLV 46 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng theo tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb t\u1edd L'Equire, Zidane l\u1ea1i h\u1ee9ng th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Man Utd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Old Trafford trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd do thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. Ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n, Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 gi\u00f4ng b\u00e3o \u1edf c\u00e1c CLB \u00f4ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, MU g\u1eb7p may khi th\u1eafng Leicester 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai kh\u00e1c, Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League 2018/19. V\u00e0 Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft, \u0111\u01b0a vinh quang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho, MU ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 cho HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen-voi-phat-bieu-ve-pogba-172-194533.html\">Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-thua-xa-man-city-va-liverpool-172-194512.html\">M.U thua xa Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca-172-194472.html\">MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ander-herrera-goi-y-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-194468.html\">Ander Herrera mang tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/darmian-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu-172-194460.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>T\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)</p>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2396","checkdouble":"194539"},{"date":"15:33 15/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.</h2><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 14/8 v\u1eeba qua, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. N\u1ebfu C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/olympic-viet-nam-vs-pakistan-8-153424042905491724090.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho \u0110T\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Sportalkorea\u00a0\u0111\u01b0a tin: Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu 2 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edd Chosun l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8: \"Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, so v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 cho k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang ghi h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u1eeba qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\">Olympic Nepal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2395","checkdouble":"194540"},{"date":"16:10 15/08","title":"U23 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \"th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n\" nh\u01b0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Nepal, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \"th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n\" \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng: Kiran Chemjong Limbu.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">U23 Nepal kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 (Asian Games, ho\u1eb7c Asiad 2018) v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Nepal, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tham d\u1ef1 Asiad v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i (b\u1ed5 sung 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5y c\u1ee7a U23 Nepal nh\u1edd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Kiran Chemjong Limbu, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n sinh n\u0103m 1990, m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i Olympic. Trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u00e9p s\u00e2n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng 63% nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 22 c\u00fa s\u00fat.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/kiran-chemjong-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kiran Chemjong c\u00f3 12 pha c\u1ee9u thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 13 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n. 12 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb Limbu c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9u thua ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c t\u1eeb pha \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ueda, ph\u00fat 67. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Limbu v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp b\u1eadt d\u1eady kh\u00e9p g\u00f3c, c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a Miyoshi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKoji Gyotoku, v\u1ecb HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a U23 Nepal, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ca ng\u1ee3i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 28 tu\u1ed5i. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Nepal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Kiran Chemjong l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i anh ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng D.</div>\r\n<h2>\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n\" c\u1ee7a Nepal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Nepal kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 thu nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Kiran Chemjong c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Limbu nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 10.000 rupee m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 2,1 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng. Trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG Nepal, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn kho\u1ea3ng 10 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 thu nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u Kiran Chemjong \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng. \u1ede Nepal, Kiran Chemjong l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t. Anh gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \"th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n\", theo c\u00e1ch g\u1ecdi \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam - c\u0169ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i U23.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRa m\u1eaft \u0110TQG n\u0103m 2008, khi m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i, Limbu ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng mang v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u C\u00fap \u0110o\u00e0n k\u1ebft 2016 (AFC Solidarity Cup), t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf Malaysia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNepal \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u - danh hi\u1ec7u duy nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n - nh\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Kiran Chemjong Limbu. Ri\u00eang \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi L\u00e0o, sau khi h\u00f2a 2-2 trong gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 hai hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Limbu c\u1ea3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 3 qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, gi\u00fap Nepal v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o 3-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Kiran Chemjong c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m. Anh t\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c v\u1ee1 x\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0m, trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG Nepal. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, Kiran Chemjong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \"th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n\" kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec c\u00e1ch ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n hay l\u00e0m truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng gi\u1ecfi. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKiran Chemjong tham d\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ef9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00ec tr\u1ebb em c\u00f3 ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 m\u1ed3 c\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c suy dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 trong x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Nepal. Sau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, \"th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n\" Kiran Chemjong Limbu l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 U23 Nepal t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Vietnamnet<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2394","checkdouble":"194545"},{"date":"16:21 15/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 15/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0110T Olympic Nepal.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Nepal \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eed th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 khi\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh Nepal. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo hy v\u1ecdng Nepal s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/binhluan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Olympic Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ec1u 15/8, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i: \u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, n\u1ebfu th\u1ebf th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Park c\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y: \u201cD\u00f9 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nepal kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Nepal.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">rong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Indonesia th\u00ec Nepal ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u00edt. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng? Hay ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c? Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi U23 Pakistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Pakistan.\u00a0T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng hay V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nepal l\u00fac 19h00, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u 16/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\">U23 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span><br>\r\nU23 Nepal, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng: Kiran Chemjong Limbu.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Nepal.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2393","checkdouble":"194546"},{"date":"17:44 15/08","title":"\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" MU b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Wilfried Zaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Crystal Palace.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park trong 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Zaha m\u1edbi k\u00fd k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Crystal Palace s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2022/23.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Tottenham ho\u1eb7c Chelsea m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Palace trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Zaha b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Zaha b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Tien-ve-Zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Zaha gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Palace</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 44 b\u00e0n trong 288 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Palace k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u0103m 2010. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf Premier League r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Fulham cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Steve Parrish c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cZaha \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn l\u00ean \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn Selhurst Park t\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi 4 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 12. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1eeba k\u00fd k\u1ebft cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai ph\u00eda. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Palace, c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Zaha. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd chia tay \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roy Hodgson sau khi \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao trong 12 th\u00e1ng qua. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Zaha nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Christian Benteke.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bakayoko-tri-an-chelsea-sau-khi-gia-nhap-ac-milan-184-194523.html\">Bakayoko tri \u00e2n Chelsea sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/than-dong-chelsea-co-the-tro-thanh-mbappe-thu-hai-172-194521.html\">Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Mbappe th\u1ee9 hai</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2392","checkdouble":"194549"},{"date":"09:17 15/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khen ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 theo d\u00f5i s\u00e1t sao c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, trang FOX Sports phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eb7ng cho V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e2y b\u00fat Gabriel Tan cho r\u1eb1ng, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang d\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/vn-15342604637281618228882.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o so v\u1edbi Pakistan v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 3-0. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho Nepal l\u1eabn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Gabriel Tan, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf con Quang H\u1ea3i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi ch\u01a1i b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u00f9 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Sohu c\u1ee7a Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD. \"Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m. M\u1ecdi con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd so v\u1edbi Pakistan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 Messi c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ASIAD. Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSiamSport c\u0169ng so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa U23 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Asiad: \"U23 Th\u00e1i Lan ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb Qatar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 l\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 nghi\u1ec1n n\u00e1t U23 Pakistan 3-0.\"<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u1edd b\u00e1o nh\u01b0 Goal phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Th\u00e1i Lan, STN Sports c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, \u0111\u01b0a tin v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng, s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfn xa.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 d\u01b0 \u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan-168-194505.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakistan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-khong-con-co-hoi-da-11m-duoi-thoi-hlv-park-hang-seo-168-194504.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\">Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2391","checkdouble":"194524"},{"date":"09:25 15/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine 19h ng\u00e0y 15/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-u23-indonesia-vs-u23-palestine-19h-ngay-158-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine l\u00fac 19h ng\u00e0y 15/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine 19h ng\u00e0y 158 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine 19h ng\u00e0y 158 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/u23-indonesia-vs-u23-palestine.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>U23 Indonesia v\u00e0 U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. Hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i, U23 Palestine th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 1, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. X\u1ebfp ph\u00eda sau l\u00e0 U23 Indonesia v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a U23 Indonesia l\u00e0 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c ngh\u00ecn C\u0110V. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, U23 Indonesia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n U23 Palestine. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinaphone 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 ch\u1ee9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, U23 Palestine h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi U23 \u0110\u00e0i Loan. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn, U23 Palestine su\u00fdt b\u1ecb U23 L\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, n\u00ean tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o U23 Indonesia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, th\u00ec c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 99% U23 Indonesia s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2390","checkdouble":"194525"},{"date":"09:40 15/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 15/8: Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/diem-tin-sang-158-paul-scholes-nhan-xet-buon-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi huy ho\u00e0ng h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau khi \u0111\u01b0a Real Madrid t\u1edbi 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00ean l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Zidane. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, sau khi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 51 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Tallinn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/lopetegui-zidane-da-la-qua-khu-voi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Lopetegui r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t sau khi Zidane ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean sau tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cZizou \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf sau khi b\u00e1n Ronaldo \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cBale l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y th\u00edch th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Bale. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Benzema. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ed1t ngay t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-180-194511.html\">Sergio Ramos: Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2389","checkdouble":"194526"},{"date":"09:43 15/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain 19h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-u23-han-quoc-vs-u23-bahrain-19h00-ngay-158-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}