><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain: 4-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5m HCV b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u1edbi U23 Bahrain. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nOlympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c mang t\u1edbi Indonesia \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh, g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a CLB Tottenham \u2013 Song Heung Min, m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i trong danh s\u00e1ch.\u00a0 Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00f3i l\u00ean, h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng ng\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi U23 Bahrain, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam \u1edf hai k\u1ef3 Asiad g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, U23 Indoneis v\u00e0 U23 UAE \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u00f2a U23 Uzbekistan (nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1) \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady U23 Bahrain v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2388","checkdouble":"194527"},{"date":"10:29 15/08","title":"Diego Simeone ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/diego-simeone-truoc-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng x\u00fac c\u1ea3m<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2 2018 gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Atletico Madri mang r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Julen Lopetegui, sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Zinedine Zidane v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/diego-simeone-truoc-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Gabi c\u1ee7a Atletico th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Courtois tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 mang \u0111\u1ebfn \"n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \"\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Atletico Madrid gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Antoine Griezmann, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Gelson Martins, Thomas Lemar hay Santiago Arias. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Diego Simeone cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t l\u00ean ngay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp\" - HLV Simeone \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: \"R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng h\u1ecd\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m ai h\u1ebft. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn theo nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Diego Simeone s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi v\u1eabn v\u01b0\u1edbng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Europa League g\u1eb7p Arsenal. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Atletico s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Atletico Madrid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-atletico-madrid-tiet-lo-ly-do-tu-choi-gia-nhap-man-utd-172-194516.html\">Sao Atletico Madrid ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-valencia-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-atletico-madrid-180-194372.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Valencia chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Atletico Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-chinh-thuc-co-tien-dao-moi-180-194137.html\">Atletico Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-bat-ngo-chuyen-huong-sang-godin-172-194125.html\">MU t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Atletico</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-tien-dao-moi-180-193893.html\">Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2387","checkdouble":"194528"},{"date":"10:57 15/08","title":"Lopetegui: \"Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Real\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/lopetegui-zidane-da-la-qua-khu-voi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi huy ho\u00e0ng h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau khi \u0111\u01b0a Real Madrid t\u1edbi 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00ean l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Zidane. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, sau khi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 51 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Tallinn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/lopetegui-zidane-da-la-qua-khu-voi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Lopetegui r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t sau khi Zidane ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean sau tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cZizou \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf sau khi b\u00e1n Ronaldo \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cBale l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y th\u00edch th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Bale. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Benzema. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ed1t ngay t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-180-194511.html\">Sergio Ramos: Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2386","checkdouble":"194529"},{"date":"10:27 15/08","title":"Klopp c\u00f3 l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/klopp-co-loi-nhan-gui-hang-tien-ve-chat-choi-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Anfield.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 g\u00e2y n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Liverpool \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 th\u00eam hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho, n\u00e2ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 khu trung t\u00e2m l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 7, bao g\u1ed3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Jordan Henderson, Georginio Wijnaldum, James Milner, Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain v\u00e0 Adam Lallana.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/klopp-co-loi-nhan-gui-hang-tien-ve-chat-choi-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay Emre Can \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u1edf Anfield v\u1eabn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng g\u1eaft gao v\u00e0 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai, HLV Jurgen Klopp qua \u0111\u00e2y mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i tinh th\u1ea7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp ra \u0111\u1ebfn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, nh\u01b0 Naby r\u1ed3i Gini v\u00e0 Millie \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ebfn 13km trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham. \u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 anh ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u2013 s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft. C\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Hendo hay Adam n\u1eefa, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Liverpool, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1i \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n sau, Liverpool h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn London l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Premier League, trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien-172-194354.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien-172-194354.html\">Liverpool h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t West Ham: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n?</span><br>\r\nLiverpool ch\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ed1n sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham, b\u1eafn ph\u00e1t ph\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u cho c\u1ea3 Premier League r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ngai v\u00e0ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2385","checkdouble":"194530"}]}